title: Braves' Sale, Tigers' Skubal win Cy Young Awards
description: The Tigers' Tarik Skubal was the unanimous choice to win the Cy Young Award in the American League, while Braves pitcher Chris Sale won in the National League.
author: David Schoenfield

title: Clark won't play in Unrivaled league, source says
description: Fever star Caitlin Clark will not play in the new 3-on-3 league Unrivaled in its inaugural season, a source with knowledge of the situation told ESPN on Wednesday.
author: Michael Voepel
